Package com.hazelcast.query

Interface PartitionPredicate<K,​V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - type of the entry key
    V - type of the entry value
    All Superinterfaces:
    Predicate<K,​V>, Serializable
    public interface PartitionPredicate<K,​V>
extends Predicate<K,​V>
    A Predicate that restricts the execution of a Predicate to a single Partition. This can help to speed up query execution since only a single instead of all partitions needs to be queried. This predicate can only be used as an outer predicate.
    See Also:
    Predicates.partitionPredicate(Object, Predicate)
